Detailed Description

Provided during an Ajax get data request and contains all the information provided by the javascript control about what data is needed.

Because the Grid, TreeGrid, Combo, Tree, and Calendar controls all do Ajax get data requests, this class contains properties relavent to a specific control such as SearchString which is used as a filter on the data rows for the combo only. Also, the SortDirection and SortColumn members are specific to the Grid and TreeGrid only.

The XmlDataHandler class uses the values in an instance of this class to create the compressed XML in response to a request for data.
